Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}譯者：白　字幕：chiman　影片：風之殤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你不是在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接用钥匙不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子小姐的个人展今天结束 我就把装饰用花要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.13,0:01:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 出展的人偶销售一空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 本月的工资也算有着落了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.76,0:01:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎么过的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上午去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.79,0:01:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从自动贩卖机买的 险些忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝吗 很暖和的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢甜的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 明明很好喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改变主意了 稍微喝一点也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像… 雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.62,0:02:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次邂逅时的白夜 黑伞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走人啦 干也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也没有加班费
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 等我收拾完这些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又买这种东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是买 是邂逅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的再浪漫也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.03,0:05:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管她的话 她搞不好会吃人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判断其与先前的连续杀人事件是同一人所为 展开搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观布子市的连续杀人事件 被害者7人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上4年前的被害者 共计13人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方对杀人鬼接二连三的恶行束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,群众开始不满…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人鬼哦 干也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说被害者达到了10人以上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但杀人鬼这个称呼还是有点夸张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这个词用得很恰当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:07:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果本案真有犯人 只能称之为杀人鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人本人肯定也很中意这个称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人鬼不需要理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲者只是死于左拐右拐的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这家伙没有杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有杀人？ 杀人犯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人和杀戮是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗 黑桐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人一生只能杀一次人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能杀一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 没什么好讨论的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是吃饭重要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼园事件之后 你带鲜花去料亭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜花…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也早就想去那家料亭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.98,0:07:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次对鲜花产生杀意了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.63,0:08:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 我已经有所觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪家随你挑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才像话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后二到三天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从撕扯的断面看来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次也是吃剩的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我先前也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从尸体的惨状看来 实在不像是人类所为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能认为是鳄鱼一类…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在这边睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以先行告退吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要去式那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前的事件和此次的杀人鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐认为是式的所为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是昨晚才发现尸体的事件 还是先前的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从遗体状态很难精确锁定作案时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.49,0:12:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够确定的 只有大致的时间带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在那个时间带 式没有不在场证明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅从事实而论 没有足够证据反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你调查了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不怎么开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起对外证明她的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有更为根本的疑问吧 黑桐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式的体内已经没有男性人格的织君了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昏睡中醒来后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她完全变成了孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:13:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时 这也意味着两仪式体内「杀人」人格的消失
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你真正的疑问是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那式应该已经没有杀人冲动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在的式又怎么解释
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是补偿行为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和浅上藤乃一案相同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不涉及生死 她就无法体会到自己的生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是用了比较危险的方法罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是这么在意 整天跟着式不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据最新情报显示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观布子市观布北町的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了连环杀人鬼的新受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据目击者称
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与先前的事件相同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现场留有大量血迹 散落着人的残肢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受害者的身份仍不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事请在听到「哔」声后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四年前 式亲口对我说 她是杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她绝对杀不了人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想杀 也杀不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一直这样坚信着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐 说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 想杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人希望你就此崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我都杀不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是为了生存而杀人 亦无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你 是为了逃避而杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要自贬身价
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只属于一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生为一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:18:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有相克的螺旋 才是你应有的终幕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏之还嫌尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起独自踏上归途 我选择了和她在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对是错 我至今都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以来到这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:21:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为受荒耶宗莲所托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归还被你忘却的两年前的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再生那份哀叹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算忘却了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但记忆确实被你录音了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.60,0:22:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事请在听到「哔」声后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是黑桐 看来你还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到这个请联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再打来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2月8日 下午4点33分 共17条留言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.78,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.30,0:23:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你每晚都到哪里鬼混去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢 这么晚了来做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来这一带搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年前 曾在两仪家门口发现尸体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那个犯人又开始行凶了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:23:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:23:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现犯人的线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.76,0:24:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的作案地点都特定在繁华街道的小巷里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人现场附近有大路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然也不乏目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次 必定有人目击到身着和服的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 干也 你没出什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.34,0:24:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.13,0:24:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.68,0:24:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道这是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.26,0:24:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮票纸是LSD
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.36,0:24:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶子是大麻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.01,0:24:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本周超过半数的遇害者都持有这个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.63,0:24:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.15,0:24:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方也还没有判明出处
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.63,0:25:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎正在年轻人间悄悄散播
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.66,0:25:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然明知可能没用
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.23,0:25:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也没有其他找寻式的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.75,0:25:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我想调查一下药和事件的关联性
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.57,0:25:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.34,0:25:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕要请长假了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.57,0:25:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.39,0:25:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐 适可而止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.43,0:25:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝姓苍崎 请转一下秋巳警官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.41,0:27:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥 找什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.86,0:27:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.46,0:27:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去别处买药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.60,0:27:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对用红票的没什么好说的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.83,0:27:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这个你知道什么吗 什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.38,0:27:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又下雨了 真头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.66,0:27:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫人怎么做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.57,0:28:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.69,0:29:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗑完药想玩找别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.50,0:30:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 想找刺激是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.54,0:30:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所愿 给你们个痛快的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.14,0:31:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京都观布子市的连续杀人事件再添新死者…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.45,0:31:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开了开了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.94,0:31:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 好点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.95,0:31:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.08,0:31:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药劲已经过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.17,0:31:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效时间大约4小时
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.75,0:31:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真有闲心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.77,0:31:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试的是最近流行的那个药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.96,0:31:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是杀人鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.41,0:31:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人身着和服？这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.61,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.68,0:31:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干也 用了这个会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.73,0:31:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不怎么推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.24,0:32:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会体会到『糖果屋』主人公的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.86,0:32:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.73,0:32:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.31,0:32:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方断定身着和服的人物是连续杀人事件的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.44,0:32:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此为重点展开搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.59,0:33:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.12,0:33:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我们见过 你还记得我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.09,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.30,0:33:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我有事问你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.50,0:33:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要找我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.95,0:33:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是女的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.22,0:33:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这无关紧要 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.27,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.86,0:33:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.19,0:33:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带不卖cocktail的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.06,0:33:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于cocktail 想必能从你那问出点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.44,0:33:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.72,0:33:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药贩子关于cocktail口风都很紧 这很怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.39,0:34:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你想问什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.50,0:34:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 用cocktail的家伙和杀人鬼有关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.49,0:34:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.38,0:34:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 你为什么要调查这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.43,0:34:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.03,0:34:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新闻上说的没错 穿和服的就是杀人鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.09,0:34:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是见到你之后
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.82,0:34:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到四个年轻男人一拥而上 和穿和服的女人动手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.25,0:34:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.24,0:34:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但新闻上说是性别不明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.69,0:34:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天这么黑 你怎么知道是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.44,0:34:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有段距离 但她的身段很美
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.88,0:34:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你认识她？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.17,0:34:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劝你还是死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.65,0:34:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是常人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.56,0:35:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人被四个男的包围 还手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.25,0:35:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手下留情…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.39,0:35:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们半死不活
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.16,0:35:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供自己反复折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.90,0:35:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正常的家伙我见过不少
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.15,0:35:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那种人还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.93,0:35:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 失望了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.74,0:35:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四名死者如你所料 是cocktail的常用者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.07,0:35:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 能请你详细讲一下cocktail的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.21,0:35:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了这些 你还想找和服女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.19,0:35:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.33,0:35:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.10,0:35:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的cocktail是LSD和大麻的新制品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.37,0:35:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.53,0:35:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玩意依存性太强 药力也很猛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.92,0:36:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种药真会搞垮身体
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.77,0:36:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不卖cocktail
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.38,0:36:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不承认血片
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.14,0:36:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血片？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.20,0:36:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血片是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.57,0:36:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.07,0:36:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法满足于cocktail的家伙用的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.52,0:36:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更上一层的cocktail
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.46,0:36:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更上一层的cocktail…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.46,0:36:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.02,0:36:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个血片和cocktail一样呈邮票状 颜色也是红的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.43,0:36:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.69,0:36:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而边缘处 渗有深红色
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.90,0:36:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你不是知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.32,0:36:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渗有深红的是供货人特制的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.57,0:36:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事很有名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.23,0:36:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.18,0:37:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但血片只卖给孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.26,0:37:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,组织底部的药贩子知道
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.84,0:37:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但上面却不以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.44,0:37:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为只是孩子随便玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.60,0:37:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以条子也不知道血片的事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.30,0:37:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 很有参考价值
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.37,0:37:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太乱来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.34,0:37:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对用血片的人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.21,0:37:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药贩子就是他们的神
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.66,0:37:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像新兴宗教一样
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.21,0:37:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.98,0:37:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道供货人的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.55,0:37:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.07,0:38:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真把所有现场都转了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.08,0:38:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.14,0:38:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.62,0:38:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有能给警方作为证据的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.42,0:38:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年开始的跨年事件
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.68,0:38:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和四年前的无故杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.68,0:38:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除杀人现场相近以外 几乎没有共同点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.99,0:38:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 搜索至今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.67,0:38:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有确凿证据 但我总认为是同一人所为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.43,0:38:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.18,0:38:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.97,0:38:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.02,0:38:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.28,0:38:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 承蒙关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.58,0:39:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.97,0:39:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件从人迹罕至的地方向繁华街区移动
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.54,0:39:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本在外界发生的忌事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.84,0:39:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今为善良市民的生活圈蒙上了阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.63,0:39:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新邻居随时可能成为被害或加害者
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.29,0:39:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市越是明亮 光照不到的地区阴影自然越是浓郁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.24,0:39:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市的阴影越深 人心的阴暗面越是浓郁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.24,0:39:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知你在寻找什么
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.08,0:39:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人心只有自己才能照亮哦 式
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.37,0:40:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜深人静之时 黑暗亦愈显厚重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.76,0:40:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以喜欢走在空无一人的街道上 是因为想要独处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.10,0:40:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或 只是想如此自欺罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.71,0:41:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.37,0:42:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.07,0:42:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…式
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.56,0:42:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.18,0:42:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.72,0:43:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦咦 奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.83,0:43:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.66,0:43:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.00,0:43:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.90,0:43:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动真格的…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.24,0:43:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和四年前简直判若两人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.53,0:44:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也随时都能杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.00,0:44:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不去跨过那条线
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.24,0:44:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明这么需要你…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.83,0:44:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有时间了 才特地来见你…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.66,0:44:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是为了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.42,0:44:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.38,0:44:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是特意把尸体留下
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.95,0:44:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.74,0:44:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为这样就能让你想起4年前
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.07,0:44:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却一直无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.20,0:44:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但似乎产生了其他效果
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.64,0:44:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 杀人鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.16,0:44:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于没有名字的我 世人赋予了这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.83,0:44:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一语中的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.72,0:44:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我高兴的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.58,0:45:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一周间就回应了他们的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.42,0:45:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人鬼就要像大家所想的 去杀人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.50,0:45:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.39,0:45:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道的 两仪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.06,0:45:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才羡慕的来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.74,0:45:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想快点获得自由 所以才想找到我这个同类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.01,0:45:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.46,0:45:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.27,0:45:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是最能理解你的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.44,0:45:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之所以做什么都无法满足
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.01,0:45:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为你在抗拒自己的起源
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.04,0:45:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要忍耐 只要做自己想做的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.67,0:45:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前也说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.53,0:45:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.17,0:45:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.77,0:45:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人 你骗人 你骗人 你骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.13,0:46:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为证据
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.33,0:46:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直注视着我的死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.24,0:46:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要压抑
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.06,0:46:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.25,0:46:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是本着自己的欲望来找我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.84,0:46:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想杀我才追来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.74,0:46:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 杀我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.46,0:46:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.94,0:46:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 你也没法恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.00,0:46:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能杀了原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.64,0:46:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维系着现在的两仪式的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.58,0:46:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 一切就都解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.16,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.62,0:46:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.20,0:47:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说杀谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.93,0:47:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.66,0:47:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.16,0:47:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.21,0:47:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是货真价实的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.31,0:47:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好说了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.77,0:47:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把妨碍者杀掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.41,0:49:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1995年4月
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.45,0:49:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我邂逅了她
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.48,0:50:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5月 来谈谈她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.23,0:50:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在见到她 我仍会浑然忘我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.08,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.43,0:50:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是注视着 我就完全疯掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.42,0:50:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的日常生活渐渐被侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.55,0:50:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一所高中的奇迹般的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.47,0:50:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多半 爱上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.61,0:50:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.18,0:50:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我讨厌弱者」
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.34,0:50:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她淡淡地说道
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.14,0:50:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪式这样拒绝了我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.43,0:50:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我讨厌弱者」
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.96,0:50:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不理解个中含义
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.91,0:50:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入夜
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.16,0:50:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次打了人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.10,0:50:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入夜
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.35,0:50:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次杀了人
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.00,0:50:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起 我再也没能入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.35,0:50:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是胆战心惊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.83,0:51:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢外出行走
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.44,0:51:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌苟延残喘的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.18,0:51:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没法照镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.52,0:51:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.12,0:51:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不想做
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.31,0:51:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.76,0:51:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是个人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.46,0:51:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七天 我发觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.72,0:51:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时死掉的 不止他一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.52,0:51:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没人告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.51,0:51:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.64,0:51:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会连同自己一起杀掉 这一单纯的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.44,0:51:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.80,0:51:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我渐渐开始发疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.78,0:51:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒耶先生说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.39,0:51:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.43,0:51:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.85,0:51:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人也是没有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.64,0:51:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是不能安心
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.25,0:51:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独一人太不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.70,0:51:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现 自己需要同样的狂人作伴
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.51,0:52:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.34,0:52:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年没见了吧 黑桐君
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.71,0:52:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想象中要快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.67,0:52:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为你要好久才能找来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.15,0:52:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有哪里疏忽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.12,0:52:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.29,0:52:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个契机
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.25,0:52:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11月
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.56,0:52:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有机会调查了一座公寓的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.77,0:52:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是普通的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.18,0:52:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然在那里住过
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.62,0:52:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定和式有关
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.16,0:52:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 白纯里绪前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.43,0:53:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒耶先生还动了这种手脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.16,0:53:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来 全被你知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.63,0:53:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 那是三年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.24,0:53:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你造访两仪式家时会碰到我 并不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.47,0:53:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了给你看她的杀人现场 才叫住了你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.64,0:53:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不能眼看着你被蒙在鼓里而成为牺牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.41,0:53:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早在4年前 前辈就开始累积罪行了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.67,0:53:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 4年前的无故杀人的犯人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.10,0:53:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是两仪式…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.74,0:53:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.15,0:53:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是前辈想做的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.46,0:54:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.08,0:54:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的胳膊…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.03,0:54:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是两仪式干的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.44,0:54:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为少一条胳膊没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.05,0:54:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却怎么都治不好
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.97,0:54:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓「杀」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.53,0:54:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.52,0:54:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要再三杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.83,0:54:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.03,0:54:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.59,0:54:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的「起源」被人唤醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.37,0:54:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被荒耶宗莲那个披着人皮的魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.97,0:54:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐君
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.12,0:54:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的起源是「吃」
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.89,0:54:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起源觉醒后的我
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.61,0:54:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有「吃」一途
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.23,0:54:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是吃人的杀人鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.92,0:54:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.33,0:55:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的情况不对劲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.12,0:55:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管这些 让我接着说
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.36,0:55:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好… 这是最后一次正常对话了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.49,0:55:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要她
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.57,0:55:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要杀人的两仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.00,0:55:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.53,0:55:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都因为有你在…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.63,0:55:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪才不肯来这边的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.91,0:55:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有她…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.87,0:55:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.30,0:55:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找橙子小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.23,0:55:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说不定有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.19,0:55:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.12,0:55:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.63,0:55:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.85,0:55:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.84,0:55:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.05,0:55:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你 无论何时都站在白纯里绪这边
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.21,0:55:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在能保持自我 也是多亏了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.30,0:56:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.78,0:56:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 不普通
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.46,0:56:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.35,0:56:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.58,0:56:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要还活着 就没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.11,0:56:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.99,0:56:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.24,0:56:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.12,0:56:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.38,0:56:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能救前辈的只有橙子小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.77,0:56:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是这样老好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.28,0:56:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.36,0:56:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就回
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.70,0:56:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情面谈
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.50,0:56:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为没救
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.99,0:57:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.51,0:58:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.78,0:58:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式 是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.59,0:58:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个… 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.59,0:58:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到哪里鬼混去了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.53,0:58:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道外面危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.47,0:59:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.19,0:59:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时住到橙子那里
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.75,0:59:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.51,0:59:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式 你又在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.64,0:59:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和干也无关
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.36,0:59:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.80,0:59:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在追杀人鬼吧 式
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.29,0:59:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.69,0:59:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 式
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.12,0:59:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.63,0:59:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能杀那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.35,0:59:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.07,0:59:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可能还有救
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.40,0:59:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要快点找到他…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.96,0:59:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见过白纯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.17,0:59:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找他？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.19,0:59:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.79,0:59:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.19,0:59:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更无法原谅他了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.83,0:59:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.15,0:59:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能杀他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.81,1:00:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.39,1:00:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打算放过难得的猎物
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.17,1:00:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是久违的偏离常轨之人
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.41,1:00:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.58,1:00:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.47,1:00:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算对方罪行累累
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.83,1:00:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人终究是不对的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.59,1:00:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经听够你的一般论了 黑桐
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.11,1:00:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白纯里绪杀的太多了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.12,1:00:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.07,1:00:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人应该被杀
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.23,1:00:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经没救了 并不普通
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.65,1:00:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 回来吧 式
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.23,1:00:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.99,1:00:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.51,1:00:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是杀了前辈 我不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.65,1:01:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.61,1:01:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.35,1:01:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我和他一样 也是杀人鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.74,1:01:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.65,1:01:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是没有杀任何人吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.43,1:01:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前只是凑巧罢了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.10,1:01:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但没有区别
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.87,1:01:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发觉到了 干也
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.80,1:01:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前的我距离杀人仅一步之遥
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.65,1:01:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为织是只知杀人的人格
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.74,1:01:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.72,1:01:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织只知道杀人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.33,1:01:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不喜欢杀人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.17,1:01:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为事故变成孤身一人的我
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.44,1:01:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管没有织 却仍渴望着杀人
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.58,1:01:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.32,1:01:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想杀人的不是死去的织
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.54,1:01:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是活下来的式
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.55,1:02:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不行 我没法回你那边
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.31,1:02:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.13,1:02:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干也不用等我了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.89,1:02:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你误会了 式
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.46,1:02:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.36,1:02:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人一生只能背负一个人的死
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.46,1:02:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很珍重此事
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.99,1:02:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更重要的是 你比谁都知道杀人之痛
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.37,1:02:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会杀任何人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.61,1:02:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑巧没有杀人？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.20,1:02:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了！
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.86,1:02:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种偶然怎么可能持续到今天
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.17,1:02:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是凭着自己的意志 一直忍了过来
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.62,1:02:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的嗜好各不相同
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.65,1:02:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式只是恰巧嗜好杀人罢了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.53,1:02:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年夏天
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.79,1:02:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在大桥上对我说过
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.10,1:02:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的杀人冲动没有想像中严重
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.54,1:03:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你的笑容 我确信
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.66,1:03:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会杀任何人
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.90,1:03:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前能 今后也能忍下去
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.11,1:03:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.49,1:03:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫绝对
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.92,1:03:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不明白的事你怎么会明白！黑桐！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.68,1:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为… 你很善良
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.00,1:03:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.33,1:03:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.77,1:03:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式啊 最讨厌你这一点了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.57,1:03:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.37,1:03:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.32,1:04:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 你很善良
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.40,1:04:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.72,1:04:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…幸福的男人
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.85,1:04:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是起源觉醒者
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.77,1:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒耶居然留下这么个无聊的饯别礼物
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.57,1:04:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是所谓「起源」啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.68,1:04:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信有前世吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.08,1:05:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不否定 也不肯定
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.51,1:05:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神或灵魂
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.51,1:05:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛开生命这一概念
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.02,1:05:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万物都在轮回转生
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.68,1:05:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前世的前世
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.24,1:05:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更遥远的前世
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.22,1:05:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿无秩序的法则回溯
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.38,1:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源源不绝的存在之线
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.50,1:05:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的灵魂的原点
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.12,1:05:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的存在的发源之处确实是存在的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.98,1:05:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.66,1:05:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里不存在什么生命
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.34,1:05:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的只是…
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.44,1:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…起始的「因」
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.40,1:05:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定事物的方向性
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.22,1:05:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这一混沌冲动
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.03,1:05:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在魔术里称为「起源」
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.01,1:05:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单说来就是本能吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.67,1:05:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.04,1:05:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「起源」终究只是「因」并不支配个人
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.79,1:06:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非因为某种契机使它觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.25,1:06:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.11,1:06:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦觉醒后 就会败给这一方向性吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.79,1:06:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白纯里绪只能重复自己的冲动
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.85,1:06:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是「吃」这一冲动也真够特别的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.96,1:06:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得荒耶会盯上他
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.76,1:06:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 黑桐
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.59,1:06:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然拥有「吃」这一起源
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.71,1:06:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白纯里绪的前世必定都是捕食者
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.90,1:06:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起源觉醒者会得到积累至今的前世
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.67,1:06:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把白纯里绪看作一个人类
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.69,1:06:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是把他看作无数野兽比较好
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.67,1:06:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在保有白纯里绪这一人格还好
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.43,1:06:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若他消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.09,1:06:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真会变成野兽的群体
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.06,1:06:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样倒也蛮有趣的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.97,1:07:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因在于把他变成这样的魔术师吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.14,1:07:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是只有前辈自己 是不会…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.80,1:07:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.59,1:07:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让起源觉醒的术
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.84,1:07:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是以施术者和受术者的同意为前提的秘术
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.56,1:07:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白纯里绪自己选择了这条路
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.93,1:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以自己的意志变成了野兽
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.86,1:07:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以自己的意志杀人
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.12,1:07:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.78,1:07:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是橙子小姐也救不了白纯前辈吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.36,1:07:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起源觉醒是追求灵魂这一形态
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.15,1:07:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进而到达根源的男人获得的终极技术
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.61,1:07:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我专攻肉体面
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.33,1:07:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对灵魂束手无策
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.17,1:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.02,1:07:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.35,1:07:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今前辈的人格还在 总能帮他做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.57,1:07:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能帮他平心静气吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.68,1:07:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.02,1:08:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.10,1:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能保持自我至今已经是奇迹了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.66,1:08:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.86,1:08:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真容易明白啊 黑桐
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.42,1:08:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不阻止你
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.35,1:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但对方可是杀人鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.70,1:08:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事交给式不就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.72,1:08:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给4年前的事件做个了断
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.03,1:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式才去追踪杀人鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.88,1:08:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.42,1:08:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人出于何种理由杀人？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.25,1:08:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对方的感情超过了自己的容量时吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.66,1:08:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是爱是恨
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.83,1:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溢出自我这一容器时
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.03,1:08:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有以某种手段消除之
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.35,1:08:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而采取极端手段时 就会杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.96,1:08:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也有人滥杀无辜啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.84,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.91,1:08:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是杀人 是杀戮
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.94,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.73,1:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人将彼此的尊严与过去置于天平之上
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.65,1:09:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消去其中一方时 才能称之为杀人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.77,1:09:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要背负杀人的意味和罪过
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.35,1:09:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但杀戮不同
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.43,1:09:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然被杀的是人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.25,1:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但杀人者没有为人的尊严和意味
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.05,1:09:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓杀人 就是一并杀掉自己
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.04,1:09:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 杀人鬼是什么
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.33,1:09:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾名思义
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.26,1:09:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人的鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.83,1:09:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和自然灾害没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.32,1:09:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能怪被卷入的一方不走运
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.14,1:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 黑桐君
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.26,1:09:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人一生只能杀一个人
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.70,1:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.99,1:10:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是式以前告诉过我的 祖父的遗言
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.96,1:10:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式一直遵守至今 如今却要舍弃它
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.10,1:10:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.52,1:10:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.55,1:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.63,1:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.96,1:10:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不便阻止你
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.61,1:10:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好 黑桐
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.57,1:10:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有缘 明天见…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.27,1:11:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.87,1:11:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥在吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.88,1:11:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打多少电话都没人接
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.19,1:11:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干也那家伙 又去那个女人那里了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.12,1:11:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接上门去找嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.67,1:11:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想当那种丧家犬
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.83,1:11:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子小姐也劝劝哥哥 快和那个女人分手吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.05,1:11:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分手吗…
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.33,1:11:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.40,1:11:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待得有点太久了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.62,1:11:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太像我 但我似乎真的很中意
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.64,1:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.32,1:11:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.85,1:11:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.39,1:13:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我精心栽培的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.00,1:13:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好浪费
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.78,1:14:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.38,1:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.07,1:14:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变回真正的你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.58,1:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪式
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.15,1:14:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会原谅…
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.73,1:14:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.69,1:15:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐！
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.02,1:15:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是他的错
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.96,1:15:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是式和织…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.63,1:15:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和另一个我的梦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.73,1:15:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只留下伤痛…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.65,1:15:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对无法得到的…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.69,1:15:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…梦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.56,1:16:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.06,1:16:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和黑桐在一起明明很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.78,1:16:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你给我看了无法得到的东西
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.30,1:16:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我变得如此不安定
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.21,1:16:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.96,1:16:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要杀
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.34,1:16:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.74,1:16:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不杀不行！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.98,1:16:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.94,1:16:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.97,1:16:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的梦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.28,1:16:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.13,1:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不能抹杀你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.45,1:16:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有让我…
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.21,1:16:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.45,1:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.96,1:16:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我杀你 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.28,1:17:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是织 最后的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.94,1:17:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能借着杀与人有所关联的织
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.78,1:17:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至没能把那句话
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.09,1:17:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达给想要传达的对象
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.32,1:17:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.42,1:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一丝…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:19.77,1:17:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…悲伤
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.68,1:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 我还活着
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.23,1:17:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.86,1:17:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织替我死了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.14,1:17:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了守护他幸福生活的梦
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.14,1:17:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你凭什么相信我
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.56,1:18:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有根据
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.06,1:18:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我今后也会相信式
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.29,1:18:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.37,1:18:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢你 所以想继续相信你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.23,1:18:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织所喜欢的 名为黑桐干也的梦
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.77,1:18:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道杀人的织
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.64,1:18:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次得到的杀人以外的感情
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.25,1:18:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让这个梦永远延续
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.62,1:18:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 希望他能记住织
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.42,1:18:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在的我 正是织的梦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.65,1:19:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.38,1:19:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人一生必定会杀一次人
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.22,1:19:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了最后让自己死去
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.15,1:19:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们仅有一次可能性
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.10,1:19:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了自己？
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.46,1:19:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是自己的生命 也不是属于自己的
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.45,1:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那爷爷呢
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.46,1:19:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.18,1:20:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经杀了好多人
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.10,1:20:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷的死没有人承受 只会去往无尽的虚空
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.11,1:20:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一次吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.50,1:20:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.60,1:20:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人 只有一次
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.60,1:20:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了别人 把它用尽后
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.93,1:20:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远无法杀死自己
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.23,1:20:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个人 求死不得
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.26,1:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.78,1:20:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别了 式
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.95,1:20:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能走的安详
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.69,1:20:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.25,1:20:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:43.05,1:20:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.56,1:21:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 这个眼神
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.81,1:21:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪式就要这样才对
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.90,1:21:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有你不行
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.66,1:22:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.90,1:22:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚也没能杀我
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.47,1:22:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明是比我更强的杀人鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.95,1:22:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.64,1:22:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却一次都没有杀过人
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.78,1:23:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒耶那种非人类除外
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.65,1:23:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.64,1:23:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真有杀人鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.99,1:23:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不是杀人鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.77,1:23:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回去
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.33,1:23:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他一起生活
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.40,1:23:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明自己能普通的活
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.54,1:23:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明必须和杀人鬼做个了断的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.46,1:23:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.91,1:23:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的错
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.11,1:24:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有他在
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.06,1:24:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我变弱了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.15,1:24:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有他
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.81,1:24:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有如今的我
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.72,1:24:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.74,1:24:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有他的话 我甚至无法生存
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.29,1:24:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.13,1:25:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗杂种
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.98,1:25:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不来这边 我会头疼的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.33,1:25:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.46,1:26:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上去除掉束缚你的原因
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.45,1:26:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 不是我想待的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.21,1:27:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.53,1:27:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…回去
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.07,1:27:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的家
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.78,1:27:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该回的…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.60,1:27:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那个地方
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.78,1:27:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过不准找我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.22,1:27:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 才会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.92,1:27:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.87,1:27:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.75,1:27:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你还蛮结实的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.49,1:27:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前 我第一次杀的家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.47,1:27:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挨了一下就死掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.55,1:27:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只挨了一下子
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.12,1:27:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打的是你就好了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.20,1:28:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不用变成杀人犯了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.51,1:28:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.61,1:28:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 你还是来找我了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.37,1:28:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然站在白纯里绪这边
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.08,1:28:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给两仪太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.81,1:28:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做我的同伴好了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.01,1:28:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不出同伴的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.57,1:28:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈的药一次都没成功不是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.74,1:28:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你居然知道这么多 黑桐
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.61,1:28:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.49,1:28:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要和我一样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.97,1:28:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但除了两仪 再也没有第二个了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.53,1:28:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能人工制造了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.90,1:28:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个仓库里种的大麻是荒耶给的
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.81,1:28:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和别处的大麻略有不同
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.13,1:28:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不会上瘾也不会产生抗性
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.30,1:29:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这种毒不会在体内分解
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.30,1:29:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用上几十次
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.69,1:29:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理性就会被完全破坏
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.06,1:29:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽到不行
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.81,1:29:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让服用了数十次的人
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.30,1:29:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了血片吗
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.66,1:29:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是「有希望的家伙」
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.91,1:29:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是沾有我的血的特制品
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.94,1:29:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人只把它当普通的药
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.57,1:29:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人受不了死掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.46,1:29:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能忍下来
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.91,1:29:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定能变成我的同类
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.62,1:29:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我要处理不想吃的尸体
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.72,1:29:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周一连杀四人的也是你吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.14,1:29:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 急死人了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.02,1:29:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意安排他们去袭击她
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.62,1:29:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪却无论如何都不跨过那一线
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.81,1:29:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的一切 都是因为你束缚着两仪
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.27,1:29:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.43,1:29:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你还在那边的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.72,1:29:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两仪就不会来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.84,1:30:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能让你死 或者来这边的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.96,1:30:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.31,1:30:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你把式…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.53,1:30:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起别人 先担心你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.34,1:31:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的大麻是通常十倍的量
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.21,1:31:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去你会死的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.59,1:31:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个 黑桐
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.53,1:31:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了它 凭自己的意志来这边的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.72,1:31:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后和我一样 变得特别
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.47,1:31:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.22,1:31:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用的话 你会死的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.20,1:32:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞下去 干也
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.38,1:32:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干也
Dialogue: 0,1:32:14.95,1:32:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吞掉它 你会死的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.97,1:32:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体抵御不过刚才吞下的药效
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.19,1:32:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的死和特别的生 到底哪边好
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.21,1:32:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连想都不用想吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.06,1:32:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.25,1:32:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉… 不怎么有趣
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.96,1:32:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢前辈所说的「普通」
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.38,1:32:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做什么「特别」 「特别的存在」
Dialogue: 0,1:32:54.81,1:32:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不普通
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.64,1:32:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么想 你都很怪
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.81,1:33:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的是你吧 前辈
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.55,1:33:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 就是你的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.40,1:33:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了人 不去正视罪过 选择了逃避
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.56,1:33:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以异常之人 当然会做异常之事为借口
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.20,1:33:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.58,1:33:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人鬼这个外号是错的
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.30,1:33:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.45,1:33:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式所怀的痛苦 你没有
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.73,1:33:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和式才不一样
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.56,1:33:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是完全相反的存在
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.08,1:33:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了人 却不承认自己的罪行
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.85,1:33:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一味逃避
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.38,1:33:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法成为杀人者 也无法成为杀人鬼的逃亡者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.66,1:33:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的真实面目 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.93,1:33:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很啰嗦耶 黑桐
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.13,1:34:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.62,1:34:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样她就能复原了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.34,1:35:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把拇指连根咬断
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.18,1:35:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.50,1:35:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的杀人鬼
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.57,1:35:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 来吧 两仪
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.55,1:35:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来让你杀人
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.31,1:35:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 来啊 来
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.57,1:35:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找别人吧 我不干
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.46,1:35:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.72,1:35:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说 我没空理你
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.17,1:36:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连你都要背叛我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.21,1:36:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.21,1:36:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为你杀人 为你走到今天 你却要抛弃我吗
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.20,1:36:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你想回干也身边吗 两仪
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.21,1:36:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你不用出去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.87,1:36:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就在这里
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.55,1:37:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.14,1:37:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还你 抱歉弄脏了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.67,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.34,1:37:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你死了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.86,1:37:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.98,1:37:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让你获得自由
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.80,1:37:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干也那家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.26,1:37:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后都摆出一副善人嘴脸 想教育我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.04,1:38:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你完全相反？笑死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.77,1:38:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 不是让你留在橙子那里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.75,1:38:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么杀了前辈绝不原谅我 而你却被他…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.87,1:38:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至死都这么蠢
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.79,1:38:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太符合你的作风了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.63,1:38:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好啊 干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.03,1:38:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说无法原谅我是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.66,1:38:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此一点 我们确实很像
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.94,1:39:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.59,1:39:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在 只是笑笑 我就好幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.61,1:39:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在 只是走走 我就好开心
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.67,1:40:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一天 我们会站到同处 你笑着说
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.69,1:40:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直希望 能有人对我说这句话
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.08,1:41:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.36,1:41:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.65,1:41:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如梦似幻的…
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.98,1:41:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岁月
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.67,1:41:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.84,1:41:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.82,1:41:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.31,1:41:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此…
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.08,1:41:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.01,1:41:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是无法原谅杀死你的这家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.94,1:43:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罢了 这副样子没法回家
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.97,1:43:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算满身泥泞的回去
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.70,1:43:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会被骂
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.23,1:43:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.13,1:43:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有你在等我
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.66,1:43:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有那如梦的岁月
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.72,1:43:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 像是一场梦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.93,1:44:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.40,1:44:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.11,1:44:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.71,1:44:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是杀了前辈 我不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.49,1:44:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是杀了前辈…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.26,1:44:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我希望你能幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.96,1:44:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不希望你再受伤
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.30,1:45:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.62,1:45:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.60,1:46:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.92,1:46:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.17,1:47:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着…
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.83,1:47:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭吗 黑桐
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.72,1:47:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了白纯哦
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.00,1:48:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随之失去了很多
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.11,1:48:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.66,1:48:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.20,1:48:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会替你背负
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.86,1:48:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.08,1:48:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏末 我对初次露出笑容的你起誓
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.72,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.39,1:48:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会替你背负罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.10,1:48:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.87,1:48:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来杀死你
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.60,1:48:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你死
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.11,1:48:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你死的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.59,1:48:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不让你孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.87,1:48:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,1:48:51.37,1:48:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说过不能杀人了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.64,1:48:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却没有遵守
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.46,1:48:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,1:48:59.01,1:49:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我真动怒了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.21,1:49:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生气了 就算哭也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.29,1:49:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.86,1:49:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算哭也不原谅我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.89,1:49:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:49:10.01,1:49:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不让你蒙混过关
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.22,1:49:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.32,1:50:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一生… 都不放开你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.31,1:56:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.96,1:56:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果你一次都没来看我呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.01,1:56:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被鲜花一顿痛骂
Dialogue: 0,1:56:50.78,1:56:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说敢在病房露面就杀了我
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.23,1:56:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我怎么去
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.24,1:56:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.10,1:57:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的左眼…
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.00,1:57:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:09.76,1:57:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真被静音说中了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.42,1:57:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个未来视的女人吗 我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:16.80,1:57:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她曾说过
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.58,1:57:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和式在一起 最后会惨到目不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:23.36,1:57:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预言应验了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.79,1:57:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是目不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,1:57:27.72,1:57:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.02,1:57:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能干什么…
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.35,1:57:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你当拐杖用啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.78,1:57:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我习惯之前的这一周 就请式多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:57:39.54,1:57:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.69,1:57:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.85,1:57:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.14,1:57:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.85,1:57:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我明天还要上学呢
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.03,1:57:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉就是了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.65,1:57:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.16,1:58:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然会让我逃课 害我都笑出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.03,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.01,1:58:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个任性的家伙
Dialogue: 0,1:58:13.56,1:58:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.55,1:58:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多年前
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.18,1:58:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就任性的喜欢上了你
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.24,1:58:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也是
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.08,1:58:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就算式不愿意
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.21,1:58:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也任性的决定要照顾你
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.33,1:58:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,1:58:31.19,1:58:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 式 你不是受不了这种话吗
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.84,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.28,1:58:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先前不知被你教训过多少次
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.94,1:58:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不是
Dialogue: 0,1:58:44.91,1:58:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说呢 干也
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.23,1:58:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的式 说她并不讨厌这个
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.14,1:59:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:08.07,1:59:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的
Dialogue: 0,1:59:10.16,1:59:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么短刀一类
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.31,1:59:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是这只掌心
Dialogue: 0,1:59:15.73,1:59:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后无论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.95,1:59:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不会放开这只手
Dialogue: 0,1:59:22.32,1:59:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的故事到此结束
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.00,1:59:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受了现在的自己和过去的式
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.51,1:59:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过着平凡的生活
